{"tid":1175831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【幾乎甩頭】俄羅斯14歲富二代打機輸了 27刀斬死朋友","createTime":"2019-05-28T22:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T06:42:28.000Z","uid":125193,"like":236,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"6f63e3c4175b80bf826af075712d85eec3aec0bb","tid":1175831,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T22:17:57.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭一名俄裔富二代與友打機輸了，一怒之下狂斬對方27刀，謀殺罪成被判監。<br />\n<br />\n14歲的圖爾達（Vasya Turda）獲從商的父親送贈電子遊戲機，邀15歲朋友波帕<br />\n（Vasya Pop）到他的豪宅一起玩。圖爾達不敵波帕，不甘受辱，拿刀斬波帕，波帕頸部中刀，逃命時被圖爾達追斬，最後身中27刀死亡。<br />\n<br />\n波帕的頭幾乎被斬掉，屍體遭圖爾達虐待。案發現場遺下一條血路。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指圖爾達指被波帕騷擾和侮辱，曾在咖啡店有女孩在場情況下剝他的褲。<br />\n<br />\n不過，<strong>法官最後裁定圖爾達謀殺罪成，判監三年半</strong>。控方要求加刑15年。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9XPCu8U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9XPCu8U.jpg&h=e8291f66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0ca2929c86bdfa0718e93bd348a6dbc5f4fb6a2","tid":1175831,"uid":191815,"like":448,"dislike":1,"score":447,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T22:20:03.000Z","msg":"3年後出嚟又一條好漢 又有爸爸養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7da3369c2f4f9f0e1bb7fe7a0f358bf8213c0dd","tid":1175831,"uid":2748,"like":349,"dislike":1,"score":348,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T22:29:19.000Z","msg":"三年半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d71806dff1a84f1a894c77f6f73efcf9cbb81c0","tid":1175831,"uid":22694,"like":187,"dislike":2,"score":185,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T22:30:53.000Z","msg":"17歲出黎重新做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613512f83894da46223f4f2d72b79a6050ff6dea","tid":1175831,"uid":63909,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTim